{
  "stem": "22856.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I found a friend who was wondering why I was not looking for a public-- for a private employment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "By that time, my monthly wages was 10,000 Polish Zloty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a friend of mine told me, I will arrange, for you, a better position in private sector.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It is Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], a very well-known person, who had, in the center of Krakow, in the main place, a book store, wholesale book.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And also, he was an editor of law literature, commentaries and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he offered me 40,000 zloty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So immediately, I changed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But that wasn't for a long time because later on, as I mentioned before, that came the order to pick up the trouble and go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "At first, the passport was-- or rather, it wasn't a passport, but it was a certificate that we are resigning of our citizenship in Poland, and we want to go to Israel, because there was no other way to go.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my brother-in-law and my wife's sister got first that certificate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they had, also, a small girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he left me his shop to liquidate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I had to sell hardware, brushes, paints, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So apart from my problem and to work in that book shop, I had to do in my free time to liquidate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Anyhow, later on, we received the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were packing and going to Israel through Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was a close transport from Vienna to Rome, and from Rome to Haifa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Well, when we came to Haifa, we had to register again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had to go through Sharalea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That is the place where all newcomer will be directed where to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We received, at the beginning, a place in, in, tents in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
